'''哈斯F1車隊'''<ref name="Haas Formula LLC">{{Cite web |url=https://opencorporates.com/companies/us_nc/1361732 |title=Haas Formula LLC |website=opencorporates.com |access-date=September 26, 2016 |archive-date=2016-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007091153/https://opencorporates.com/companies/us_nc/1361732 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|'''Haas F1 Team'''}}），舊稱為'''哈斯方程式'''（{{lang-en|'''Haas Formula'''}}）、'''哈斯賽車發展'''（{{lang-en|'''Haas Racing Developments'''}}）和'''-{zh-hk:烏拉爾卡利;zh-cn:乌拉尔钾肥;zh-tw:烏拉爾卡利}-哈斯F1車隊'''（{{lang-en|'''Uralkali Haas F1 Team'''}}）<ref name="dallara"/><ref name="usa today">{{cite news|title=Gene Haas: No reason U.S.-based Formula One team can't succeed|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/motor/formula1/2014/04/14/gene-haas-formula-one-team-success-organization/7703033/|first=Jeff|last=Gluck|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today Sports]]|publisher=Gannett Company|date=2014-04-14|accessdate=2014-04-15|language=en|archive-date=2014-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415154326/http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/motor/formula1/2014/04/14/gene-haas-formula-one-team-success-organization/7703033/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Forza Rossa"/><ref name="haas rd">{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/112160|title=NASCAR team boss Gene Haas plans new Formula 1 squad for 2015|first1=Dieter|last1=Rencken|first2=Jonathan|last2=Noble|work=Autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2014-01-16|accessdate=2014-04-16|language=en|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403103907/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/112160|dead-url=yes}}</ref> <ref name="uralkali name">{{Cite web |url=https://www.haasf1team.com/news/uralkali-announced-haas-f1-team-title-partner |title=Uralkali Announced as Haas F1 Team Title Partner |access-date=2021-03-04 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304082016/https://www.haasf1team.com/news/uralkali-announced-haas-f1-team-title-partner |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一支由[[全國運動汽車競賽協會|全國運動汽車競賽協會]][[斯普林特盃系列賽|斯普林特盃系列賽]]車隊擁有人{{link-en|吉尼·哈斯|Gene Haas}}於2014年4月成立的[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]車隊。車隊原先預計於[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年賽季]]首次登場，<ref name="yahoo">{{cite news |url=https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/nascar%E7%9A%84gene-haas%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97f1%E5%8F%83%E8%B3%BD%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-031410109.html |title=NASCAR的Gene Haas取得F1參賽資格 |work=[[Yahoo!奇摩|Yahoo!奇摩]] |publisher=Racingnet |date=2014-04-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428075837/https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/nascar%E7%9A%84gene-haas%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97f1%E5%8F%83%E8%B3%BD%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-031410109.html |archivedate=2014-04-28 |accessdate=2014-04-28 |language=zh-tw }}</ref><ref name="新浪">{{cite news |url=http://sports.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/120/4/2/874851/1.html |title=FIA將在今天確認哈斯成為第12支F1車車隊 |work=[[新浪|新浪]] |publisher=新浪體育 |date=2014-04-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428080530/http://sports.sina.com.hk/cgi-bin/nw/show.cgi/120/4/2/874851/1.html |archivedate=2014-04-28 |accessdate=2014-04-28 |language=zh-hk }}</ref><ref name="Forza Rossa">{{cite web|title=FIA WMSC statement, Marrakech, 11 April 2014|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-friday-11-april-marrakech|publisher=Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile|work=FIA.com|date=2014-04-11|accessdate=2014-04-11|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004095437/https://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-friday-11-april-marrakech|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="two new">{{cite news|title=Formula 1 could have two new teams in 2015 - Bernie Ecclestone|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/113313/|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Media Group|date=2014-04-06|accessdate=2014-04-07|language=en|quote="They will be accepted," he said about the Haas entry. "We have also accepted another team as well."|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408033301/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/113313|dead-url=yes}}</ref>不過他們之後選擇延後至[[2016年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2016年]]再參賽。<ref name="Debut 2016">{{cite web|url=http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/161097.html|title=Haas confirms debut will be in 2016|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2014-06-04|accessdate=2014-06-04|language=en|archive-date=2014-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606221414/http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/161097.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

總部與全國運動汽車競賽協會斯普林特盃系列賽參賽隊伍{{link-en|史都華-哈斯車隊|Stewart-Haas Racing}}一同設立於[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]][[坎納波利斯|坎納波利斯]]<ref name="Kannapolis"/>，但兩個車隊被視為各自獨立的團隊。車隊同時也於[[英國|英國]][[牛津郡|牛津郡]][[班伯里|班伯里]]設立第二前進基地，目的是為了在歐洲地區賽季期間的比賽能夠更方便的挪用賽車。<ref name="dallara"/>此外[[法拉利车队|法拉利车队]]在2020年12月宣布将在其总部意大利[[马拉内罗|马拉内罗]]开设“哈斯中心”，以期加强对哈斯车队的技术支持。<ref name="HaasHub2020">[https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/ferrari-setting-up-haas-hub-in-maranello/4930483/ Ferrari setting up Haas F1 hub in Maranello] {{Wayback|url=https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/ferrari-setting-up-haas-hub-in-maranello/4930483/ |date=20210525011015 }}.Motorsport.2020-12-22.[2021-03-06].</ref>

==歷史==
===籌備與首個賽季（2016年）===
哈斯車隊是自[[美國F1車隊|美國F1車隊]]申請參賽[[2010年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2010年賽季]]失敗後首次提出參賽的美國[[一級方程式賽車車隊列表|車隊]]，<ref>{{cite news|last=Beer|first=Matt|title=FIA fines and disqualifies US F1|publisher=Haymarket Group|work=Autosport.com|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/84715|date=2010-06-24|accessdate=2014-04-16|language=en|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416193047/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/84715|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同時也是自{{le|1985年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1985 Formula One season|1985年賽季}}和{{le|1986年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1986 Formula One season|1986年賽季}}出賽的{{link-en|哈斯·羅拉車隊|Haas Lola}}後首支美國參賽車隊。哈斯·羅拉由[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]老闆{{le|泰迪·梅耶|Teddy Mayer}}及與吉尼·哈斯沒有血緣關係的{{le|卡爾·哈斯|Carl Haas}}所持有。

[[File:Romain_Grosjean_2016_Malaysia_FP2_1.jpg|thumb]]在[[2016年馬來西亞大獎賽|馬來西亞站]]駕駛{{le|VF-16|Haas VF-16}}。]]

在[[瑪魯西亞車隊|瑪魯西亞車隊]]於[[2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2014年賽季]]期間倒閉並拍賣其資產後，哈斯買下了該隊位在班伯里的總部，以做為他們的前進基地。<ref>{{cite news|title=Haas F1 on schedule for 2016 debut after key acquisitions|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/31823683|accessdate=2015-03-22|work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2015-03-10|language=en|archive-date=2016-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131062849/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/31823683|dead-url=no}}</ref>

